file: HookDispatcher.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\HookDispatcher"
type: readonly final class
summary: The HookDispatcher class orchestrates the execution of registered hook subscribers by mapping hook names to their corresponding handlers. It leverages a subscriber registry to identify relevant hooks and an event dispatcher to trigger the associated logic with provided context data.
